      "content": "Elara: (her voice flickering with static) Total peace... that sounds so much easier than this constant fear of disappearing bit by bit. It’s like the more I try to hold on, the more it hurts. Is it... is it wrong to want to just give in? To stop trying to be \"someone\" and just let the erasure happen?",
